<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Truchseß von Baldersheim, Vogt von Windsheim und Ritter</head><p>Der Rat erteilt dem Fleischhacker Hans Stöcklein bis Laetare Geleit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_411" id="205r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_411_r1l1">Hanſen Truchſeſʒ von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l2">Balderſheim vogt cʒu vvındſheım <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_411_r1l3">Lıeber her Hans Als Jr vns <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von 
<del rend="strikethrough"> de </del> eins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l4">fleiſchackers wegen genant <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Stöcklein / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> dauon </del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l5"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vormals cʒemal nihts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l6">dauon gevviſʒt / vnd dancken ew <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrs ſchreibens <expan>fleıſʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l7">vnd alſo laſʒen vvir ew vviſſen / vvenn das iſt / daʒ derſelb hans </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l8">Stöcklein <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd dem Suntag Letare cʒu <expan>Mıtvaſte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchierſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l9">herkümt / So ſol er ein ſleht geleẏte hie beẏ vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l10">vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu vns vnd von vns ongeuerde / vnd vvo vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l11">auch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb vnd dinſt beweiſen <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> das teten vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_411_r1l12">gern / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> valentini Anno xıj<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_411" id="205r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Truchsesz von Baldersheim, vogt czu Windsheim,
                            <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Hans, als ir uns <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                        eins fleischackers wegen, genant <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Stöcklein,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        vormals czemal nihts davon gewiszt und dancken ew
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrs schreibens
                                <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>; und also laszen wir ew wissen,
                        wenn das ist, daz derselb Hans Stöcklein
                            <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und dem <app><note><q type="date">suntag letare czu
                                    <expan>mitvaste<ex>n</ex></expan> schierst</q>13.03.1412</note></app> herkümt, so sol er ein
                        sleht geleyte hie bey uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czu uns und von uns ongeverde. Und wo
                        wir auch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb und dinst beweisen
                                <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das teten wir gern.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Valentini anno
                            xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
